Introduction

WJSN CHOCOME (우주소녀 쪼꼬미) is a sub-unit of the group WJSN/Cosmic Girls Under Starship Entertainment and Yuehua Entertainment. The group consists of: Luda, Soobin, Dayoung and Yeoreum.
